



15,01                           14The Shadow

15,01                   14Darkest secrets locked within,
15,01                   14Forth from this a life begins,
15,01                   14This vilest, blackest side,
15,01                   14Which most do hide,
15,01                   14Causes us to lose our minds

15,01                   14Pain and terror mounts and grows,
15,01                   14From our hearts a spring doth flows,
15,01                   14Water black and purest evil,
15,01                   14Evoking human lusts primeval,
15,01                   14Succumbing to our dark desires.
































